oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Hackberry Ramblers Performance - 1999-12-03 - Tape 2
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The tape is of a performance by the Hackberry Ramblers (musical group). The tape was recorded on December 03, 1999. The tape is part two of two.
